    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This reliable sedan is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior looks great with only a few minor cosmetic blemishes from normal use, such as small stone chips on the hood and light scratches near the door handles. The interior is clean and comfortable, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a complete service history. It\u2019s a solid, dependable vehicle that is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
