      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking for a new home for this reliable beauty! It\u2019s been such a fantastic ride and still has so much life left in it. It\u2019s been well-loved, runs like a dream, and is totally ready to hit the road with its next owner. Whether you need a solid daily commuter or something for weekend trips, this car has got you covered! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
