    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec E46 M3 powered by the high-strung S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for precise torque distribution. The double-VANOS system has been professionally shimmed and serviced, and the rear subframe mounting points have been inspected and reinforced to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. Suspension geometry is maintained by a refreshed set of bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including valve clearances and rod bearing clearances\u2014are within factory tolerances. A mechanically sound, high-performance icon for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 32500.0,
