    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a reliable, stylish daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, though upon close inspection, you will find minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scuff on the rear passenger-side bumper. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring supple leather seating with only light bolster wear on the driver's side. All electronic components\u2014including the dual-zone climate control, premium sound system, and navigation\u2014function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound; it recently underwent a full fluid service, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. The tires are matching continentals with approximately 70% tread remaining. Included are two sets of keys and a comprehensive folder of service records from the last four years. This is a solid, honest example of a well-loved car that is ready for its next chapter.",
